g.text: Environment: Apple's environment is unmatched. Customers get tremendous advantages simply by having
several Apple devices. That leads to repeat customers over the long-term.
AI: Apple's AI efforts have been close to null so far.Over the long-term, artiﬁcial intelligence has the power
to create new devices that could substitute the smartphone.
Vision Pro: Apple Vision Pro is a good product that, when it reaches a lower price, has incredible use cases
that could lead to an even bigger moat.
